WEBVTT

00:10.596 --> 00:11.252
MADDY [DREAMING]: It's broken.

00:11.287 --> 00:12.460
It's broken.

00:12.495 --> 00:13.254
It's almost time.

00:13.289 --> 00:13.875
It's almost time.

